data.name: sqlDataEducation.SelectCommand
data.value: SELECT tPDSEducation.*, tPDSEducationLevel.educLevelName FROM tPDSEducation LEFT JOIN tPDSEducationLevel ON tPDSEducationLevel.educLevelCode = tPDSEducation.educLevelCode WHERE EIC = @paramCode AND isVerified = 1 AND pageNo = 1 ORDER BY tPDSEducationLevel.orderNo
